---
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
const datum = "5 July 2026";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | VinoMartino"
  description="How VinoMartino handles your personal data."
  locale="en"
  alternates={{ nl: '/privacy/', en: '/en/privacy/' }}
>
  <section class="legal container">
    <article class="legal-body">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="update-datum"><em>Last updated: {datum}</em></p>

      <p><strong>Controller:</strong> VinoMartino (see <a href="/en/colofon/">imprint</a> for company details)<br />
      <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@vinomartino.com">privacy@vinomartino.com</a></p>

      <h2>What data do we process?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Statistics</strong>: we use Plausible Analytics, a cookie-free service that stores no personal data and no IP addresses.</li>
        <li><strong>Anonymous click tracking</strong>: when you click an affiliate link, we record the link type, partner platform, page and timestamp. No name, email address or IP address.</li>
        <li><strong>Contact</strong>: if you email us, we use your name and email address only to answer your enquiry.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>See the <a href="/en/cookies/">cookie statement</a>.</p>

      <h2>Third parties</h2>
      <p>If you click through to a booking or affiliate partner (such as CJ Affiliate, TradeTracker, GetYourGuide or Stay22), that party is responsible for processing your data and their own privacy policy applies.</p>

      <h2>Retention periods</h2>
      <p>Anonymous click records are retained for a maximum of 12 months. Contact details are deleted once your enquiry has been handled, and within 6 months at the latest.</p>

      <h2>Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access, rectification, erasure and to object to processing. Email <a href="mailto:privacy@vinomartino.com">privacy@vinomartino.com</a>; we will respond within 30 days. Complaints can be submitted to the <a href="https://www.autoriteitpersoonsgegevens.nl" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Netherlands Data Protection Authority</a>.</p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>The current version of this statement is always available on this page.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0;
  }
  .legal-body {
    max-width: 44rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .legal-body h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 1.6rem + 1.5vw, 2.875rem);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }
  .legal-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: var(--space-10) 0 var(--space-3);
  }
  .legal-body p,
  .legal-body ul {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--inkSoft);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .legal-body ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  .legal-body li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  .legal-body a {
    color: var(--burgundy);
  }
  .legal-body a:hover {
    color: var(--burgundyDeep);
  }
  .legal-body strong {
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .update-datum {
    color: var(--inkFaint);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: var(--space-6) 0;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }
  th {
    background: var(--paperDeep);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 0.625rem 0.75rem;
    text-align: left;
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  td {
    padding: 0.625rem 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ruleSoft);
    color: var(--inkSoft);
  }
  tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  code {
    background: var(--paperDeep);
    padding: 0.125rem 0.375rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
</style>
